[I] A system daemon to allow session software to update firmware

[T] A system daemon to allow session software to update firmware.

[U] https://fwupd.org

[A] LVFS by Richard Hughes
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] base/tool
[F] CROSS

[E] add jinja2
[E] opt vala
[E] opt flashrom
[E] opt gi-docgen graphviz
[E] opt libftdi1
[E] opt openimageio
[E] opt systemd

[L] LGPL
[V] 2.1.3

[D] 0c55a91b8feee50166af607e6de213cc39798eaac81f46a02f36492c fwupd-2.1.3.tar.xz https://github.com/fwupd/fwupd/releases/download/2.1.3/

pkginstalled gobject-introspection || var_append mesonopt ' ' -Dintrospection=disabled
var_append mesonopt ' ' '-Defi_binary=false -Dplugin_uefi_capsule_splash=false'
var_append mesonopt ' ' -Dtests=false
